<paragraph id="6247DD4AFFAEE719FB6FFC92AF339987" blockId="0.[1241,2124,830,1454]" pageId="0" pageNumber="462">• Medium-sized, rabbit-like rodents, with large eyes and ears, long and dense hair, and long brushy, well-furred tail.</paragraph>
<caption id="36878DC2FFAEE719FB6FFC15AFA999FF" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6585602" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6585602" box="[1245,1452,953,982]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6585602/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="462" targetBox="[1483,2008,977,1165]" targetPageId="0">
