</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6247DD4AFFAEE719FB6BFB61AD6E9F11" blockId="0.[1241,2124,830,1454]" pageId="0" pageNumber="462">• Semi-arid and arid plains to grasslands, low shrublands, and high-elevation steppes in western and southern South America from sea level to 6000 m.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6247DD4AFFAEE719FB68FAEFAD689F49" blockId="0.[1241,2124,830,1454]" box="[1242,1901,1347,1376]" pageId="0" pageNumber="462">• 3 genera, 6 species, at least 8 extant taxa.</paragraph>
